               <p>On the 20th of November, in the evening, I lost these two looking glasses; I saw them about an hour before in the farther part of my shop; on a table; my wife cried out; I ran immediately; the man had got to the next court; she said, that was the man, and I collared him immediately.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to.)</p>
